OL,3,CCampaign for Real Ale names pub of the
OL,4,Cyear
OL,6,FThe Bristol and District Campaign for
OL,7,FReal Ale has named a Chipping Sodbury
OL,8,Ftaproom its pub of the year.
OL,10,FEvery year CAMRA invites local members
OL,11,Fto nominate pubs for consideration in
OL,12,Fthe branch Pub Of The Year competition.
OL,14,FFinalists of the nomination stage are
OL,15,Fthen judged against various nationally
OL,16,Fdesignated criteria to decide the
OL,17,Fresult.
OL,19,FThis year, The Horseshoe in Chipping
OL,20,FSodbury claimed the top spot.
