OL,6,FLandlord Matt Lewis has only been
OL,7,Fthere a couple of years, but said they
OL,8,Fregularly appear on CAMRA's Good Beer
OL,9,FGuide.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's incredible. It's been a
OL,12,Flong time coming, we've been in the
OL,13,FGood Beer Guide for so long now it's
OL,14,Fabout time we won pub of the year.
OL,15,FIt's just an incredible feeling."
OL,17,FIn terms of dealing with challenges in
OL,18,Fthe industry, Matt said putting on a
OL,19,Frange of events has really helped.
