OL,6,FHe said: "We're just doing what we
OL,7,Fcan, we're plodding on by. Lots of
OL,8,Fdifferent events, live music every
OL,9,FSunday, brewery tours, and just being
OL,10,Fpart of the community."
OL,12,FOn Friday 17 May the pub will be
OL,13,Fhosting a pig race for charity.
OL,15,FLoyal customer Simon Kohn said it's a
OL,16,Fplace you can "feel very comfortable
OL,17,Fin".
