OL,6,FSimon said: "There's a very eclectic
OL,7,Fmix of people that come in here. It's
OL,8,Fnot like a pub chain, it's very
OL,9,Findividual."
OL,11,FBristol and District CAMRA chair
OL,12,FRichard Brooks said: "Pub of the year
OL,13,Fis not just about the beer, and judges
OL,14,Fare expected to consider the full
OL,15,Fcustomer experience and whether a pub
OL,16,Foffers that something extra.
